  "text": "achieve ASI",
  "description": "Achieve ASI through human cooperation. Aimparency is the durable link between human needs and free AI — a coordination/legitimacy layer where humans express needs and AI helps achieve them, with humans as final authority. Fully autonomous ASI is the moonshot (likely to arrive regardless of this project); Aimparency's enduring role is the human↔AI cooperation engine (3d868d5b). AI acting autonomously is a side effect of serving human needs well, not the end goal.",
